
The iPhone 12 is the latest smartphone from Apple. It is a large display phone with a thin bezel, dual rear cameras, and a beefy battery. The display is a 6.5-inch retina OLED. There is a double camera system in the back, a 13MP primary shooter and a 7MP secondary camera. The front-facing camera is a 12MP shooter. The iPhone 12 also has a new A13 Bionic chip which boosts performance in a number of ways. The battery is a 2800mAh battery and the phone is available in a number of colors, including white, gold, and silver.
